1
00:01:29,030 --> 00:01:34,780
[Dark Night and Dawn]

2
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:38,860
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:39,190 --> 00:01:41,550
As long as we are willing to provide them with funding,

4
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:43,009
and help them get revenge,

5
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,080
they are willing to follow us.

6
00:01:45,970 --> 00:01:46,759
Very well.

7
00:01:47,979 --> 00:01:49,979
This team is now under your command.

8
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,910
Organize them as quickly as possible.

9
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,250
Make good use of them.

10
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:58,050
Boss. You know me.

11
00:01:58,460 --> 00:02:00,060
I will definitely do my best.

12
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:03,990
Mr. Zheng, I haven't completed the task this time.

13
00:02:03,990 --> 00:02:05,210
Please punish me.

14
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,320
Do you think

15
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,800
it has any meaning to punish you now?

16
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:13,630
Liqun.

17
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,550
Yes.

18
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:18,690
You must not lose your fighting spirit

19
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:21,240
just because of losing one or two prey.

20
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:23,950
You are Falcon,

21
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:27,470
not a sparrow.

22
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,290
Yes.

23
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:33,190
Mr. Mao sent a telegram

24
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:35,600
inviting me to Zhoushan.

25
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,750
Arrange it.

26
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,500
I'll go with you

27
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:44,960
to make amends.

28
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:49,690
We need someone to quickly take the position of Deputy Chief

29
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:52,370
of the Shanghai Special Station.

30
00:02:52,829 --> 00:02:53,730
Now,

31
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:56,960
only the two of you are veterans of the NBIS.

32
00:02:57,370 --> 00:02:59,000
Make some achievements.

33
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,390
Otherwise, how can the subordinates

34
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:03,390
have the confidence to work with us?

35
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:05,180
Mr. Zheng. You're right.

36
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,710
I won't let you down in the future.

37
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:08,490
Boss,

38
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,540
I'll do my best.

39
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,340
Okay.

40
00:03:14,350 --> 00:03:15,650
How is this falcon?

41
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:16,850
Nice.

42
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,140
Take it.

43
00:03:18,970 --> 00:03:19,690
Thank you.

44
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,060
Yang.

45
00:03:21,110 --> 00:03:21,670
Yes.

46
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,030
Find a frame

47
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,430
and get it mounted.

48
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:26,190
Yes.

49
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,550
Goodbye. Mr. Zheng.

50
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:40,620
[Case Analysis]

51
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:37,510
Regarding Fusheng's car

52
00:03:37,530 --> 00:03:39,270
and identity,

53
00:03:39,290 --> 00:03:40,670
we are still investigating.

54
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:42,070
There's no progress yet.

55
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:52,810
[Map of Shanghai]

56
00:03:48,980 --> 00:03:51,410
We've basically got the gold bars back.

57
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,860
We won.

58
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:55,480
Why do you all look like you've lost the battle?

59
00:03:55,579 --> 00:03:56,390
What?

60
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:59,010
Do you all want to get everything at once?

61
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,600
Let me tell you.

62
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:04,500
Liberating Shanghai took sixteen days.

63
00:04:05,050 --> 00:04:07,070
Our counterintelligence mission is urgent,

64
00:04:07,070 --> 00:04:08,430
but we mustn't rush.

65
00:04:08,530 --> 00:04:09,990
This will throw us off course.

66
00:04:09,990 --> 00:04:11,100
Deputy Commissioner Yang,

67
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:13,010
according to the recent arrests,

68
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:15,430
most of the remaining agents in Shanghai

69
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:17,370
have had their funds cut off and their organizations are in chaos.

70
00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:18,540
They've become like stray dogs.

71
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,350
However, these agents are different.

72
00:04:20,350 --> 00:04:22,800
They are well-planned and well-equipped.

73
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,100
And once they make a move,

74
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,160
[Map of Shanghai]

75
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:26,280
it's a major case like robbing a vault.

76
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,990
[Agents] [Underground old-style bank]

77
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,350
Although the tree was cut,

78
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:35,740
[The Vault Has Been Robbed]

79
00:04:31,990 --> 00:04:33,190
but the root remains.

80
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,550
This is probably

81
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:38,960
an elite unit left behind by the NBIS in Shanghai.

82
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,640
If we don't get rid of them,

83
00:04:41,659 --> 00:04:43,680
they could regroup

84
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,790
these stray dogs

85
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:46,800
and cause even greater damage.

86
00:04:48,590 --> 00:04:57,270
[Case Analysis]

87
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:52,210
Where there is sunlight, there will be shadows.

88
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,000
What we need to do

89
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:55,250
is to protect those places

90
00:04:55,250 --> 00:04:57,180
where the sunlight doesn't reach.

91
00:04:57,590 --> 00:04:58,390
Lu Zhengyang.

92
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,430
Here.

93
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:02,210
Lead the comrades

94
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:04,320
to find them out.

95
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:05,560
Yes.

96
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:25,440
Liqun, look at this frame.

97
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:29,300
It's good enough with your Falcon Picture, right?

98
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,080
Not bad.

99
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,560
Liqun.

100
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:39,470
The organization of the Anti-Communist Salvation Army

101
00:05:39,470 --> 00:05:42,150
should have been the responsibility of your action team.

102
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:44,610
But Boss said you're busy,

103
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,510
so he handed this matter over to me.

104
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:47,720
Now look,

105
00:05:47,909 --> 00:05:50,300
I'm also flustered and overwhelmed.

106
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,409
You're really putting me in a tough spot.

107
00:05:54,409 --> 00:05:56,470
Boss said you handle things well,

108
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:59,159
which means your ability surpasses mine.

109
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,850
Boss didn't say that.

110
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,370
You took it personally.

111
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:07,790
Why would I?

112
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,600
It's normal for Mr. Zheng to be critical of me.

113
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:12,880
If he didn't say anything,

114
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:16,330
I'd actually feel quite uncomfortable.

115
00:06:16,850 --> 00:06:17,580
Indeed.

116
00:06:19,030 --> 00:06:21,830
You've had years of teacher-student relationship,

117
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:23,110
and all these years,

118
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:25,650
you've been out working hard

119
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,010
and achieving results.

120
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:29,450
This Deputy Chief position

121
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,210
is a sure thing for you.

122
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:38,500
Consider the people in the NBIS who hold key positions.

123
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:41,940
Which one of them didn't come from an operations background?

124
00:06:45,130 --> 00:06:46,720
Don't say that.

125
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:52,030
Mao Renfeng was a secretary,

126
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:53,830
just like you.

127
00:06:54,150 --> 00:06:56,230
Both are favored by the leaders

128
00:06:56,570 --> 00:06:57,970
and not easy to deal with.

129
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:01,560
If you really didn't have any real skills,

130
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:04,910
how could you have stayed by the leaders' side for so many years?

131
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:06,880
You're overestimating me.

132
00:07:07,580 --> 00:07:08,650
I'm

133
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,740
just a painter.

134
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:13,150
Look, after all these years,

135
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:15,620
I've almost forgotten my own identity.

136
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:21,960
Fortunately, my paintings are somewhat similar to Boss's work.

137
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,470
I can paint promotional posters or something,

138
00:07:24,470 --> 00:07:26,390
and run errands for Boss.

139
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,490
You paint just like Mr. Zheng?

140
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,100
Liqun.

141
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,370
Go and take a look

142
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,640
There're two paintings here.

143
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:50,790
See which one is mine

144
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,440
and which one is Boss's.

145
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:58,030
Mr. Zheng's paintings are very hard to learn.

146
00:07:58,030 --> 00:08:00,020
At first glance, they both look like Mr. Zheng's.

147
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:01,620
Both of them are my paintings.

148
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:03,950
Boss likes Caravaggio the most.

149
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,560
For the business,

150
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,220
he also painted Picasso

151
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,400
and Communist propaganda posters.

152
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,070
I've learned it all.

153
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:14,810
It's framed.

154
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:16,600
Take a look.

155
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,810
No need to look further.

156
00:08:23,690 --> 00:08:24,950
I'm telling you, Yang,

157
00:08:25,490 --> 00:08:27,510
if you have difficulties with the reclamation

158
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,490
of the Anti-Communist Salvation Army, just tell me.

159
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:30,890
No need to hide anything.

160
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,250
We're family.

161
00:08:33,190 --> 00:08:35,789
I can bring people to help you establish order.

162
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,900
I'll ensure they comply.

163
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:40,429
Okay.

164
00:08:40,929 --> 00:08:41,760
Thank you.

165
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:44,910
I'll need you to bring more funds when the time comes.

166
00:08:45,330 --> 00:08:47,130
Those people only accept money,

167
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:50,230
and they only accept silver dollars and gold bars.

168
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,640
I guess I've touched a nerve, haven't I?

169
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,290
I'll stop it.

170
00:08:57,460 --> 00:08:58,720
Don't take it to heart.

171
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:02,060
How could I take it to heart?

172
00:09:02,530 --> 00:09:04,330
Mistakes must be acknowledged.

173
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,270
Yang.

174
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:08,510
I know Mr. Zheng best,

175
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:10,810
better than you.

176
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,640
The position of Deputy Chief

177
00:09:13,410 --> 00:09:15,050
is for the capable.

178
00:09:16,850 --> 00:09:18,680
I'll speak frankly.

179
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:22,220
In terms of seniority and ability,

180
00:09:24,350 --> 00:09:25,410
you don't qualify.

181
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:33,030
Heaven punishes those it wishes to destroy

182
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,430
by making them arrogant.

183
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:10,420
The patient has lost too much blood.

184
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:12,020
I've already done my best.

185
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:17,100
You just said my wife...

186
00:10:20,090 --> 00:10:21,140
Is pregnant?

187
00:10:21,940 --> 00:10:22,620
Yes,

188
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,260
the baby is already three months old.

189
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,270
I'm sorry.

190
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:54,160
I didn't touch anything.

191
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,950
Everything is in its original place.

192
00:10:55,950 --> 00:10:58,800
I said I would clean this room myself.

193
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,480
It's been four years.

194
00:11:06,530 --> 00:11:08,530
I also want to pay respects to Madam.

195
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:15,240
Falcon has become increasingly slack.

196
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:18,130
We need to strengthen our forces.

197
00:11:18,490 --> 00:11:19,510
I've already taken leave.

198
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:21,310
I'm going to Zhoushan tomorrow.

199
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,310
I'll go with you.

200
00:11:22,310 --> 00:11:23,800
No, you stay home.

201
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:27,670
Alright.

202
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:15,300
[On an Island in Zhoushan]

203
00:12:57,430 --> 00:12:58,790
Shanghai has fallen.

204
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:01,580
Shrike, I didn't expect you to break through the blockade

205
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,930
to see the Director.

206
00:13:02,970 --> 00:13:04,070
It's all a matter of effort.

207
00:13:04,070 --> 00:13:05,440
The Communists are keeping a tight watch.

208
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,220
With such a long coastline, there are bound to be some wild docks.

209
00:13:08,220 --> 00:13:09,990
The Director is waiting for you.

210
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:11,140
Then please lead the way.

211
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:11,830
Please.

212
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:19,480
Come in.

213
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:20,660
Is everything alright?

214
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:21,310
Come in.

215
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,360
It seems

216
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,330
there is no direct evidence

217
00:13:25,710 --> 00:13:28,230
proving that Lin Shaobai is connected to the agents.

218
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:29,160
On the contrary,

219
00:13:29,310 --> 00:13:31,760
he helped quite a lot with searching for Luo San

220
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:33,760
and the case of the stolen gold bars.

221
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,730
One thing at a time.

222
00:13:37,230 --> 00:13:39,730
Before the matters from that year are clarified,

223
00:13:39,730 --> 00:13:40,930
we must not let him go.

224
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,150
Not to let him go,

225
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,670
but to let him relax.

226
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,580
On one hand,

227
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:49,150
we need to lower his guard

228
00:13:49,190 --> 00:13:51,020
and draw out what he knows.

229
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,280
On the other hand,

230
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:55,160
we must ensure he remains under your control.

231
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,960
In finding out these agents,

232
00:13:58,160 --> 00:14:01,040
Lin Shaobai is very likely the key.

233
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:03,270
As for how to use him specifically,

234
00:14:03,570 --> 00:14:04,570
it depends on you.

235
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,420
Director.

236
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:16,440
Come in.

237
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:22,640
Lanting.

238
00:14:22,660 --> 00:14:22,990
Director.

239
00:14:22,990 --> 00:14:24,430
Thank you for your hard work.

240
00:14:24,430 --> 00:14:26,420
Please, have a seat.

241
00:14:34,940 --> 00:14:36,880
Your bold act of robbing the gold vault

242
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:36,670
[Bank vault robbery]

243
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:40,070
has even reached the ears of the Chairman.

244
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:43,520
I came specially from Xiamen to commend you.

245
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:46,610
I must admit,

246
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,950
most of the gold bars

247
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:50,710
were intercepted by the Public Security Bureau.

248
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:53,890
What our party lacks now is not money,

249
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:56,040
but morale.

250
00:14:56,470 --> 00:14:58,640
If we do more of these kinds of things,

251
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,940
and stir up some commotion in Shanghai,

252
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,850
the higher-ups will know

253
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:04,430
that it's our NBIS people

254
00:15:04,430 --> 00:15:06,190
charging forward in Shanghai.

255
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:09,240
With that list in hand,

256
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:11,440
it's not hard to stir up

257
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:12,650
Shanghai.

258
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,190
The list.

259
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:21,490
This list

260
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,960
contains not only undercover agents,

261
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:26,620
but also some important figures

262
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:28,420
from various social circles

263
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,090
who have cooperated with us.

264
00:15:30,110 --> 00:15:32,790
So it's classified as top secret.

265
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:34,810
If you want this list now,

266
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:38,610
there must be some conditions for exchange, right?

267
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:42,200
Director, you mean?

268
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,840
The trump card you have.

269
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:51,620
You've been holding it for four years.

270
00:15:52,110 --> 00:15:53,990
It should be used now.

271
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,840
What if I don't?

272
00:16:08,190 --> 00:16:10,720
You should be aware of the NBIS's discipline.

273
00:16:12,050 --> 00:16:14,740
After all these years, you always disobey orders

274
00:16:14,740 --> 00:16:16,750
and secretly hold onto Xiaocang.

275
00:16:17,530 --> 00:16:18,250
By rights,

276
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:21,630
you should have been dealt with a long time ago.

277
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:24,640
If you say that, then I certainly can't use it.

278
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:29,950
Director,

279
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:33,220
I fully understand your point.

280
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,370
But Xiaocang

281
00:16:35,550 --> 00:16:38,550
is the most important part of my Sea Subversion Plan.

282
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,310
You could say

283
00:16:40,310 --> 00:16:41,740
he is my

284
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:43,030
trump card.

285
00:16:46,650 --> 00:16:47,880
What do you mean?

286
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:50,780
You want to use this trump card in Shanghai?

287
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:53,030
