597
00:30:20,650 --> 00:30:21,910
They're really cheaper than outside.

598
00:30:21,910 --> 00:30:23,510
Of course, they're cheaper.

599
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:24,500
And,

600
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,350
