608
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:35,790
I want a box of malted milk.

609
00:30:35,790 --> 00:30:37,380
Four boxes of luncheon meat.

610
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:39,640
[Lin's Home]

611
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:38,350
Great!

612
00:30:38,350 --> 00:30:39,720
Four boxes of luncheon meat.

613
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,790
Register first.

614
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:44,140
