615
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:45,070
Line up, line up.

616
00:30:45,340 --> 00:30:46,270
Line up, line up.

617
00:30:46,270 --> 00:30:48,110
[Lin's Home]

618
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:49,560
Line up, line up.

619
00:30:51,540 --> 00:30:53,030
