627
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,210
Falcon.

628
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,820
I don't need you to show mercy.

629
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,290
Your life is cheap.

630
00:31:19,290 --> 00:31:21,810
If it weren't for the fact that we've worked together before,

631
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:22,870
who would save you?

632
00:31:28,210 --> 00:31:30,070
This mission was completed well.

633
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,280
Do you like it?

634
00:31:40,250 --> 00:31:43,310
From now on, you'll officially become my subordinate.

635
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:48,610
The people from the investigation team were killed by you.

636
00:31:51,860 --> 00:31:53,270
If you work with us,

637
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,580
you need to follow the rules.

638
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,980
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask.

639
00:31:58,140 --> 00:31:59,230
You lied to me.

640
00:32:00,190 --> 00:32:02,140
You said you were dealing with the Japanese,

641
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,870
but why are the Communists in the Western-style building?

642
00:32:03,870 --> 00:32:05,220
The deed is done.

643
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:06,980
It doesn't matter.

644
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:13,470
The investigation team was established by the Japanese.

645
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:15,240
You want to cover this up.

646
00:32:15,670 --> 00:32:18,530
Anyone can be killed. Just don't touch Lin Shaobai.

647
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:20,510
What if there's an investigation later?

648
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:21,770
I'll make him back off.

649
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:24,920
Falcon, I warn you,

650
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:26,640
if you touch my brother,

651
00:32:26,990 --> 00:32:29,310
I don't care if you're from the NBIS or CISB.

652
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:30,470
I won't let this go.

653
00:32:37,810 --> 00:32:38,920
Cut the crap.

654
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,980
I won't mix with you anymore.

655
00:32:45,450 --> 00:32:47,770
You know my knife is sharp.

656
00:32:48,590 --> 00:32:50,410
If there's anything else to confess, hurry up.

657
00:32:50,410 --> 00:32:51,950
You won't get another chance soon.

658
00:32:51,950 --> 00:32:53,220
You're finished.

659
00:32:54,130 --> 00:32:55,370
In Shanghai,

660
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:58,230
you're like rats that can't be seen in the light.

661
00:32:58,230 --> 00:33:00,360
You only deserve to hide in the sewers.

662
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:01,430
Even if I die,

663
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:04,030
I won't be used by you to harm others.

664
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,040
Don't be so rough.

665
00:33:09,110 --> 00:33:10,300
Let go, let go.

666
00:33:10,850 --> 00:33:12,270
Let's talk this over.

667
00:33:20,030 --> 00:33:22,730
I could have handed you over to Mao Sen,

668
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:25,150
but I didn't.

669
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:27,810
You owe me another life.

670
00:33:28,510 --> 00:33:30,190
What do you want exactly?

671
00:33:33,670 --> 00:33:36,570
Do you know who my favorite painter is?

672
00:33:38,080 --> 00:33:38,960
An Italian.

673
00:33:39,490 --> 00:33:40,780
Caravaggio.

674
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:43,710
He lived only 39 years.

675
00:33:44,190 --> 00:33:46,110
Although he lived only 39 years,

676
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,800
his life was enchanting.

677
00:33:50,380 --> 00:33:52,460
He had a famous painting called

678
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,910
"David with the Head of Goliath."

679
00:33:55,190 --> 00:33:56,470
Who was Goliath?

680
00:33:56,490 --> 00:33:57,920
The Vanguard.

681
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,740
A magical giant.

682
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,710
Your expression now

683
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:05,940
is so much like Goliath.

684
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:07,480
It's identical.

685
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:12,260
I don't understand what you're saying.

686
00:34:12,310 --> 00:34:15,130
Anyway, I want to resurrect Goliath

687
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:18,530
and make the Philistines turn the tide.

688
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:22,139
You don't understand now,

689
00:34:22,179 --> 00:34:24,230
but think it over and come back to me.

690
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:31,239
[Morning News]

691
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:39,530
[Morning News]

692
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:45,610
[Morning News]

693
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,880
Just kill him.

694
00:34:48,010 --> 00:34:54,929
[Morning News]

695
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:53,710
This person is loyal and righteous.

696
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:55,679
I really like him.

