00:36:27,990 --> 00:36:29,590
Stop! Don't run!

704
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,840
We're on the same side. Don't shoot.

705
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:56,190
Wait!

706
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:02,550
