707
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,190
Where are you going?

708
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:08,650
Come here. Come over here.

709
00:38:08,710 --> 00:38:10,310
Where are you going? Listen to me. Stay calm.

710
00:38:10,310 --> 00:38:10,710
Listen to me.

711
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:11,850
I'm going to the Commissioner.

712
00:38:11,850 --> 00:38:13,050
Keep your voice down.

713
00:38:13,490 --> 00:38:16,380
I've seen the perpetrator of the explosion. It's not them.

714
00:38:16,380 --> 00:38:17,490
What do you mean?

715
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:20,890
They just randomly picked two people to impersonate the culprits.

716
00:38:20,890 --> 00:38:22,150
They kill them at will.

717
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:24,170
Can you wake up?

718
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:27,370
There was no explosion, only self-immolation.

719
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,920
The Director has said it many times.

720
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:30,750
Do you think the case will continue

721
00:38:30,750 --> 00:38:32,390
