722
00:38:32,390 --> 00:38:33,900
Listen to me. Sign it.

723
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:36,190
If we sign, we'll be safe. Okay?

724
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:42,800
You didn't see what's in the photos.

725
00:38:42,890 --> 00:38:44,210
Give it up.

726
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:45,640
If we investigate further,

727
00:38:45,640 --> 00:38:47,870
the Japanese will kill us to keep us silent.

728
00:38:47,870 --> 00:38:49,930
The KMT agents won't spare us either.

729
00:38:49,930 --> 00:38:50,890
The Communists will also

730
00:38:50,890 --> 00:38:52,270
be indirectly harmed because of us.

731
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:53,600
Don't you want to live?

732
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:55,470
Three people from the investigation team are already dead.

733
00:38:55,470 --> 00:38:56,860
If we investigate further,the next to die will be you and me...

734
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,660
Are you involved in this matter?

735
00:39:01,830 --> 00:39:02,810
Shaobai.

736
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:05,650
Listen to me.

737
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,730
We are not iron walls.

738
00:39:10,150 --> 00:39:11,070
We are just

739
00:39:11,790 --> 00:39:12,670
minor policemen

740
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:14,670
who can't even control our own life.

741
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:17,820
Listen to me. Sign it.

742
00:39:18,430 --> 00:39:20,490
It's better for both of us if you sign.

743
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:21,580
Okay?

