770
00:41:19,430 --> 00:41:20,490
No one has seen him.

771
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:21,870
Take the photo.

772
00:41:22,110 --> 00:41:23,190
Distribute this money

773
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:25,010
to your newsboy friends.

774
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:26,770
If you can find this person,

775
00:41:26,790 --> 00:41:28,390
the money in the wallet is yours.

776
00:41:28,390 --> 00:41:29,760
Alright, Officer Lin.

777
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:31,140
I'm not a police officer anymore.

778
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:32,060
